title.text: How it Works | Delphia Help Center

content.text: How it Works | Delphia Help Center Go to Delphia All Collections The App How it Works How it Works The Delphia App 101 Written by Cameron Westland Updated over a week ago Delphia is a totally new breed of investment firm that wants to turn your data into an unfair investing advantage. We plan to put collective data to work to make our artificial intelligence smarter, so it can invest in the right companies before everyone else. All to give you an investing edge and earn you the returns you deserve.HOW IT WORKSCreate an accountDownload the Delphia app, take a few minutes to set up your account and you’re all set!Tell us a bit about yourselfYou don’t need a finance degree to use Delphia. That’s the best part! Just fill out a quick profile and we’ll take care of everything for you, creating a personalized strategy that works for you.Deposit funds directly from your bankLink your bank account to Delphia and you can start investing however much you want in seconds. Then we put our AI to work to start investing on your behalf.Keep track of your progressDelphia makes it easy to keep track of your investments and returns. Sign in to the app anytime to check your portfolio, historical trends, daily returns and more.SupportContact us via chat if you have any questions, ideas, or suggestions.
